<br>
I disagree. Even augmented, nothing buyable competes with Time gear. I've seen the 100/100 bp from Takish with a hp mod in each of its 3 slots for a 210 bp. Very impressive, but my usual tank has an unmodified 250 hp breastplate, with almost twice it's ac, an aggro gaining effect, and probably will mod it to 290 or higher. No player without at least elemental gear is going to be able to augment themselves to be on par with someone heavily Time geared, and that'll stay the same until Time-level guilds start beating the hard LDoN raids.<br>
<br>
As for things being too easy- raid forces can be worn down, and are, but not in the same ways they were back in velious. As a cleric, mana can get pretty tight on extended AE fights if you have to try to keep a group up, and the timing you talked about still exists and is probably a lot more important in the high end of PoP than it ever was in Luclin (especially with pre-nerf mod rods). And as someone that's organized raids for years, from kunark dragons to Quarm, high end PoP is vastly more difficult to coordinate and organize than it was during velious. Guilds with massive manpower but no coordination tend to stumble, hard, once they reach Plane of Time, but very tightly organized ones tend to burn through the first 3 phases and most of the 4th in their first week. <br>
<br>
Anyways, I'm just a lurker here, since I only play FV with lowbies alts, but thought I'd chip in. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=larraquemeleagrance>Larraque Meleagrance</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://members.rogers.com/fvresidents/smile.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Radical Dreamer</span><br>  Posts: 2326<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(9/25/03 2:33 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4101.topic&index=14>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.ajmyatt.pwp.blueyonder.co.uk/avatars/homerofborg.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Say what?</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>But you obviously quit before the expansion where they added the sense of humour. <hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
